      "content": "it just feels so heavy though. like staying and \"defying\" it is just a way of prolonging the inevitable misery. it's like being forced to watch a tragedy unfold in slow motion for decades when you could just step out of the theater now. doesn't it feel a bit cruel to demand someone keep suffering through a dying world just for the sake of \"defiance\"?",
